::Shredder/Zenyak::

Shredder rolls to the left, one of the stray shots hitting him in the leg. 
This female obvioustly didn't know what was good for her. He fires back.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Zenyak chuckles as he hears Liono's transmission in the predacon base. The 
fool, he thinks to himself, relying on things like loyalty and mercy would be 
his downfall...
